ight:6},alt:""},directionsLink:"https://maps.app.goo.gl/zUQ3sBzFzS2MAUg3A",address:"9 St Vincent St, London W1U 4DA, United Kingdom"},{title:"Lincoln Square",city:"Manchester",country:"gb",primaryImage:{src:{src:"/_next/static/media/LincolnSquare_Large_Desktop.5ce3a1bc.jpg",height:1946,width:2600,blurDataURL:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",blurWidth:8,blurHeight:6},alt:""},secondaryImage:{src:{src:"/_next/static/media/LincolnSquare_Small_Desktop.78f4788c.jpg",height:2391,width:2e3,blurDataURL:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",blurWidth:7,blurHeight:8},alt:""},primaryImageMobile:{src:{src:"/_next/static/media/LincolnSquare_Large_Mobile.a1275f1d.jpg",height:750,width:1005,blurDataURL:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",blurWidth:8,blurHeight:6},alt:""},directionsLink:"https://maps.app.goo.gl/4qyG3K5NQ1o8vJXi8",address:"1 Brazennose St, Greater Manchester, M2 5BP, United Kingdom"},{title:"Colmore Row",city:"Birmingham",country:"gb",primaryImage:{src:a_,alt:""},secondaryImage:{src:{src:"/_next/static/media/ColmoreRow_Small_Desktop.c665abaf.jpg",height:2255,width:1881,blurDataURL:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",blurWidth:7,blurHeight:8},alt:""},primaryImageMobile:{src:a_,alt:""},directionsLink:"https://maps.app.goo.gl/VDfM8VqQoWjYAXPv8",address:"10 Livery Street, Birmingham, B3 2NU, United Kingdom"},{title:"\xd6stermalmstorg",city:"Stockholm",country:"se",primaryImage:{src:{src:"/_next/static/media/Ostermalmstorg_Large_Desktop.ff4c4a93.jpg",height:1845,width:2466,blurDataURL:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",blurWidth:8,blurHeight:6},alt:""},secondaryImage:{src:{src:"/_next/static/media/Ostermalmstorg_Small_Desktop.cc1c096b.jpg",height:1503,width:1254,blurDataURL:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",blurWidth:7,blurHeight:8},alt:""},primaryImageMobile:{src:{src:"/_next/static/media/Ostermalmstorg_Large_Mobile.2ac0bba4.jpg",height:750,width:1005,blurDataURL:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",blurWidth:8,blurHeight:6},alt:""},directionsLink:"https://maps.app.goo.gl/npTb9RCpr4YtKYMw8",address:"Sibyllegatan 35, 114 42 Stockholm, Sweden"}],ax=[{name:"Hilding",quote:(0,k.nx)({en:"Superb experience, from start to finish. It truly felt like the healthcare of the future. Advanced measurements and sensors, the design of the premises, the staff's approach, and the visualization and reports afterwards. 10 out of 10.",sv:"Super upplevelse, fr\xe5n start till slut. Det k\xe4ndes verkligen som framtidens sjukv\xe5rd. Avancerade m\xe4tningar och sensorer, designen i lokalen, personalens bem\xf6tande och visualisering och rapporter efter\xe5t. 10 av 10."})},{name:"Bj\xf6rn",quote:(0,k.nx)({en:"Finally, an absolutely fantastic solution to get all the results in one visit. By having annual checks and comparisons, one can see changes and detect unwelcome health conditions early. You get a thorough analysis of your health status by a doctor.",sv:"\xc4ntligen, en helt fantastisk l\xf6sning att f\xe5 alla resultat p\xe5 ett och samma bes\xf6k. Genom \xe5rlig kontroll och j\xe4mf\xf6relse kunna se f\xf6r\xe4ndringar och tidigt uppt\xe4cka ov\xe4lkommet h\xe4lsotillst\xe5nd. Man f\xe5r en grundlig analys av h\xe4lsol\xe4get av l\xe4kare."})},{name:"Jessica",quote:(0,k.nx)({en:"The most complete health examination I have been to. Incredibly competent doctor who immediately talked about all the tests, results, and analysis. So amazingly interesting and exciting to be able to follow one's health over time. Extra fun that Neko is close to research and collects data also for the future!",sv:"Den mest kompletta h\xe4lsounders\xf6kning jag varit p\xe5. Oerh\xf6rt kompetent l\xe4kare som direkt ber\xe4ttade om alla prover, resultat och analys. S\xe5 makal\xf6st intressant och sp\xe4nnande att kunna f\xf6lja sin h\xe4lsa \xf6ver tid. Extra kul att Neko Ligger n\xe4ra forskningen och samlar in data \xe4ven f\xf6r framtiden!"})},{name:"Jesper",quote:(0,k.nx)({en:"A check-up that everyone should do annually. For a small fee, you get a relatively comprehensive health check. Moreover, the staff is very competent and pleasant. 